Architecture Diagram
User submits job details
        ↓
/api/generate reads forge_rules from Supabase
        ↓
Builds dynamic system prompt (base + doctrine + learned rules)
        ↓
Claude Sonnet 4 generates proposal
        ↓
Stores in proposals table (outcome = 'pending')
        ↓
User sends proposal → logs outcome via /api/outcome
        ↓
Every 3+ outcomes: /api/learn analyzes patterns
        ↓
Claude extracts one new rule → writes to forge_rules
        ↓
Next generation reads updated rules automatically
        ↓
Win rate improves → repeat
